devilspie2:
devilspie2: Devilspie2 is a window matching utility, allowing the user to 
devilspie2: perform scripted actions on windows as they are created. For 
devilspie2: example you can script a terminal program to always be positioned  
devilspie2: at a specific screen position, or position a window on a specific 
devilspie2: workspace. Devilspie2 is based on the program Devilspie 
devilspie2: by Ross Burton
